Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.10,0:01:58.81,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}貴方以上なんていないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.81,0:02:00.89,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}You're my missing piece
